Task:
{{ task }}

Tool Candidates:
{% for tool in tool_candidates %}
<tool>
- server_name: {{ tool["server_name"] }}
- tool_name: {{ tool["tool_name"] }}
- tool_description: {{ tool["tool_description"] }}
- input_schema: {{ tool["tool_input_schema"] }}
</tool>
{% endfor %}

Previous task and result context (chronological order):
{% for task_result in previous_task_results %}
<task_result>
- task: {{ task_result["task"] }}
- result: {{ task_result["result"] }}
</task_result>
{% endfor %}

Iteration results from previous iterations of current task:
{% for iteration_result in iteration_results %}
<iteration_result>
    - executed_task:
    {{ iteration_result["subtask"] }}
    - result:
    {{ iteration_result["result"] }}
</iteration_result>
{% endfor %}
